Templates.template:
new sap.sac.df.FilterField(
	"${sId}", // string
	{
		id: ${id}, // sap.ui.core.ID
		models: ${models}, // object
		bindingContexts: ${bindingContexts}, // object
		objectBindings: ${objectBindings}, // object
		metadataContexts: ${metadataContexts}, // object
		validationSuccess: [function (oEvent) {}, this], // function|array
		validationError: [function (oEvent) {}, this], // function|array
		parseError: [function (oEvent) {}, this], // function|array
		formatError: [function (oEvent) {}, this], // function|array
		modelContextChange: [function (oEvent) {}, this], // function|array
		tooltip: ${tooltip}, // sap.ui.core.TooltipBase
		customData: [${customData}], // sap.ui.core.CustomData[]
		layoutData: ${layoutData}, // sap.ui.core.LayoutData
		dependents: [${dependents}], // sap.ui.core.Element[]
		dragDropConfig: [${dragDropConfig}], // sap.ui.core.dnd.DragDropBase[]
		fieldHelpDisplay: ${fieldHelpDisplay}, // (sap.ui.core.Element|string)
		blocked: ${bBlocked}, // boolean
		busy: ${bBusy}, // boolean
		busyIndicatorDelay: ${1000}, // int
		busyIndicatorSize: ${sap.ui.core.BusyIndicatorSize.Medium}, // sap.ui.core.BusyIndicatorSize
		visible: ${bVisible}, // boolean
		fieldGroupIds: [${fieldGroupIds}], // string[]
		validateFieldGroup: [function (oEvent) {}, this], // function|array
		delegate: ${delegate}, // object
		dataType: ${"sap.ui.model.type.String"}, // string
		dataTypeConstraints: ${dataTypeConstraints}, // object
		dataTypeFormatOptions: ${dataTypeFormatOptions}, // object
		editMode: ${sap.ui.mdc.enums.FieldEditMode.Editable}, // sap.ui.mdc.enums.FieldEditMode
		required: ${bRequired}, // boolean
		display: ${sap.ui.mdc.enums.FieldDisplay.Value}, // sap.ui.mdc.enums.FieldDisplay
		textAlign: ${sap.ui.core.TextAlign.Initial}, // sap.ui.core.TextAlign
		textDirection: ${sap.ui.core.TextDirection.Inherit}, // sap.ui.core.TextDirection
		placeholder: ${""}, // string
		valueState: ${sap.ui.core.ValueState.None}, // sap.ui.core.ValueState
		valueStateText: "${valueStateText}", // string
		width: ${width}, // sap.ui.core.CSSSize
		multipleLines: ${bMultipleLines}, // boolean
		maxConditions: ${-1}, // int
		conditions: [${conditions}], // object[]
		label: ${""}, // string
		delegate: ${"...see text or source"}, // object
		showEmptyIndicator: ${bShowEmptyIndicator}, // boolean
		_valueHelpEnabled: ${b_valueHelpEnabled}, // boolean
		_ariaAttributes: ${[object Object]}, // object
		_operators: [${_operators}], // string[]
		content: ${content}, // sap.ui.core.Control
		contentEdit: ${contentEdit}, // sap.ui.core.Control
		contentDisplay: ${contentDisplay}, // sap.ui.core.Control
		fieldInfo: ${fieldInfo}, // sap.ui.mdc.field.FieldInfoBase
		fieldHelp: ${fieldHelp}, // (sap.ui.mdc.ValueHelp|string)
		valueHelp: ${valueHelp}, // (sap.ui.mdc.ValueHelp|string)
		ariaLabelledBy: [${ariaLabelledBy}], // (sap.ui.core.Control|string)[]
		liveChange: [function (oEvent) {}, this], // function|array
		press: [function (oEvent) {}, this], // function|array
		submit: [function (oEvent) {}, this], // function|array
		operators: [${operators}], // string[]
		defaultOperator: "${defaultOperator}", // string
		propertyKey: ${""}, // string
		additionalDataType: ${additionalDataType}, // object
		change: [function (oEvent) {}, this], // function|array
		metaPath: "${metaPath}" // string
	}
)
Templates.name: sap.sac.df.FilterField
Templates.helpDescription: The FilterField control is used to filter data based on the conditions. The conditions are managed in the corresponding {@link sap.ui.mdc.condition.ConditionModel ConditionModel}.

Templates.name: sap.sac.df.Grid.fireOnCellClick
Templates.helpDescription: Fires event {@link #event:onCellClick onCellClick} to attached listeners.
